window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The exciting, titillating, and action-filled conclusion to <i>Captive in the Dark</i>. </p> <p>What is the price of redemption? </p> <p>Rescued from sexual slavery by a mysterious Pakistani officer, Caleb carries the weight of a debt that must be paid in blood. </p> <p>The road has been long and fraught with uncertainty, but for Caleb and Livvie, it's all coming to an end. </p> <p>Can he surrender the woman he loves for the sake of vengeance? </p> <p>Or will he make the ultimate sacrifice?</p>"; 
